data.description: Riverview at Monterra offers beautiful new homes for sale in Antioch, CA. Choose from 4 single-family home designs with 4 bedrooms, 2-3 car garages, and up to 2,766 sq. ft. Enjoy a community with a low tax rate, no HOA, close to commute routes and the new Hillcrest BART station. Offered By: K. Hovnanian CA Land Holdings, LLC
